00:32:36.780 --> 00:32:39.740
when people I know or people
I love or my people are

00:32:39.740 --> 00:32:42.290
in the audience, I often feel--

00:32:42.290 --> 00:32:43.670
do the stakes feel higher?

00:32:43.670 --> 00:32:45.350
In a way, that's
sweet but scary.

00:32:45.350 --> 00:32:48.380
And I sort of feel that here
because I feel like probably

00:32:48.380 --> 00:32:50.750
because you're my
people in many ways.

00:32:50.750 --> 00:32:54.700
So thank you for being
here and making me nervous.

00:32:54.700 --> 00:32:57.990
And I am so honored to be here.

00:32:57.990 --> 00:33:01.804
