01:00:18.910 --> 01:00:19.900
That's not right.

01:00:19.900 --> 01:00:20.800
So whatever.

01:00:20.800 --> 01:00:24.552
That's old battles
from the 1990s.

01:00:24.552 --> 01:00:26.010
So I was using the
word transsexual

01:00:26.010 --> 01:00:32.020
to talk about that, how
those feminist politics,

01:00:32.020 --> 01:00:34.810
feminist theory,
feminist movement,

01:00:34.810 --> 01:00:37.600
apply to trans women
and other people.

01:00:37.600 --> 01:00:41.470
And on the other hand, we're
talking about how involving,

01:00:41.470 --> 01:00:45.220
including trans women's
lives and experiences changed

01:00:45.220 --> 01:00:46.010
