01:03:00.460 --> 01:03:01.710
So there wasn't those.

01:03:01.710 --> 01:03:03.164
There wasn't Tumblr.

01:03:03.164 --> 01:03:04.080
There wasn't Facebook.

01:03:04.080 --> 01:03:05.890
There wasn't any
of those things.

01:03:05.890 --> 01:03:09.390
And so I was writing
without those things.

01:03:09.390 --> 01:03:13.080
I was relying on books
and magazine articles.

01:03:13.080 --> 01:03:15.640
And those are things
