01:03:17.360 --> 01:03:22.530
So some of the weakness from
the [? manifest ?] that I feel--

01:03:22.530 --> 01:03:25.510
and I kind of feel
embarrassed that sometimes,

01:03:25.510 --> 01:03:27.670
some of the universities
