cutting-edge piece, which

01:03:31.050 --> 01:03:32.020
it's not.

01:03:32.020 --> 01:03:34.980
Is something that was written
at a certain historical moment

01:03:34.980 --> 01:03:36.480
that is not now.

01:03:36.480 --> 01:03:38.910
And I think it could be
beneficial if people actually

01:03:38.910 --> 01:03:40.050
