01:04:04.470 --> 01:04:11.160
on one hand, we have rapid
and just explosive explosion

01:04:11.160 --> 01:04:13.590
of the trans movement
and trans awareness,

01:04:13.590 --> 01:04:16.530
trans visibility over
the last 20 years.

01:04:16.530 --> 01:04:18.900
That was so much
hidden at the time.

01:04:18.900 --> 01:04:23.220
But it's much more visible
