01:04:23.220 --> 01:04:24.850
so many trans
people who are out,

01:04:24.850 --> 01:04:28.530
so many trans people who are in
the media, and who [INAUDIBLE]..

01:04:28.530 --> 01:04:31.710
And also there are so
many trans allies who

01:04:31.710 --> 01:04:33.450
are feminist and non-feminists.

01:04:33.450 --> 01:04:35.580
