have spread about [? trans ?]

01:04:54.075 --> 01:04:57.780
[? issues ?] in general,
the transfeminism--

01:04:57.780 --> 01:05:03.630
it's like sharp awareness of
the interaction between trans

01:05:03.630 --> 01:05:07.830
women's experiences with the
